Preface:
    Evolubots is a simple alife simulator, that the main objective is
verify how simple organims using few resources to obtain information
from the "world" can create extremely good solution to problems that
they have to be alive (like the humans and all the diferent especies).

Requeriments:
    *Pygame (tested with v1.9.1)
    *Pyfann (tested with v2.1~beta)
    *Scipy  (tested with v0.7.2)
    -Install using apt:
     *sudo apt-get install python-pygame python-pyfann python-scipy


Watch out:
    *This program can create artificial intelligence and use your
internet connection to dominate the world. Proceed at your own risk.
